item.title: Thieving stall
item.dc:creator: @sexy_slay sexy slay
item.description:
@sexy_slay wrote:

Changing a stall amount is actually quite easy, first start by opening client.java. Then seach for the amount that you recieve when you steal from the stall. Every source is alittle different but you may see something similar to this.

case 4460: if(actionTimer == 0) { TheifStall2("table", "You Steal 400k !", 80, 160*playerLevel[17], 995,400000, 53, 0x340); actionTimer = 2; } else { sendMessage("Your massing , click once per 2 secs"); } break;
Then lets say you want to make it from 400k to 200k, you do the following

case 4460: if(actionTimer == 0) { TheifStall2("table", "You Steal 200k !", 80, 160*playerLevel[17], 995,200000, 53, 0x340); actionTimer = 2; } else { sendMessage("Your massing , click once per 2 secs"); } break;
If this helps you then GREAT, but if it doesnt i am sorry that i could not be of further help.
-Sexy Slay
